  <entry>
    <title>关于多表的增删改查记录</title>
    <link href="/2022/11/02/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%A4%9A%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%9E%E5%88%A0%E6%94%B9%E6%9F%A5/"/>
    <url>/2022/11/02/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%A4%9A%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%9E%E5%88%A0%E6%94%B9%E6%9F%A5/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="关于多表的增删改查记录"><a href="#关于多表的增删改查记录" class="headerlink" title="关于多表的增删改查记录"></a>关于多表的增删改查记录</h1><blockquote><p>今天在做 瑞吉外卖 项目的时候，涉及到了关于多表一起查询修改的操作，记录一下整个过程</p></blockquote><h2 id="当前情况描述"><a href="#当前情况描述" class="headerlink" title="当前情况描述"></a>当前情况描述</h2><blockquote><p>当前有两张表，分别是dish表和dish_flavors表</p></blockquote><p>dish表如下</p><table><thead><tr><th>名</th><th>类型</th><th>注释</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>id</td><td>bigint</td><td>主键</td></tr><tr><td>name</td><td>varchar</td><td>菜品名称</td></tr><tr><td>category_id</td><td>bigint</td><td>菜品分类id</td></tr><tr><td>price</td><td>decimal</td><td>菜品价格</td></tr><tr><td>code</td><td>varchar</td><td>商品码</td></tr><tr><td>image</td><td>varchar</td><td>图片</td></tr><tr><td>……</td><td>……</td><td>……</td></tr></tbody></table><p>dish_flavors表如下</p><table><thead><tr><th>名</th><th>类型</th><th>注释</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>id</td><td>bigint</td><td>主键</td></tr><tr><td>dish_id</td><td>bigint</td><td>菜品</td></tr><tr><td>name</td><td>varchar</td><td>口味名称</td></tr><tr><td>……</td><td>……</td><td>……</td></tr></tbody></table><blockquote><p>此时前端传给后端的数据为</p><p>{name: “青椒肉丝”, price: 2000, code: “”, image: “789266bf-3678-41ca-98ce-d9e2a71d77f6.png”,…}</p><p>categoryId: “1413384954989060097”</p><p>code: “”</p><p>description: “123123”</p><p>flavors: [{name: “甜味”, value: “[“无糖”,”少糖”,”半糖”,”多糖”,”全糖”]”, showOption: false}]</p><p>  0: {name: “甜味”, value: “[“无糖”,”少糖”,”半糖”,”多糖”,”全糖”]”, showOption: false}<br>image: “789266bf-3678-41ca-98ce-d9e2a71d77f6.png”</p><p>name: “青椒肉丝”</p><p>price: 2000</p><p>status: 1</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>可以看到上面的数据不仅包含dish表的一些相关数据，其中还包含了一项flavors，很明显这就涉及到了dish_flavors表的相关数据。</p><p>但是我们在后台只有两个类，Dish和DishFlavors，那么该怎么解决这个问题呢？</p></blockquote><h2 id="问题解决"><a href="#问题解决" class="headerlink" title="问题解决"></a>问题解决</h2><blockquote><p>既然缺少一个既包含Dish又包含DishFlavors的类，那么我们就自己新建一个这样的类</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * dto:数据传输对象</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> */</span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">@Data</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">DishDto</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Dish</span> &#123;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> List&lt;DishFlavor&gt; flavors = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">ArrayList</span>&lt;&gt;();<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> String categoryName;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> Integer copies;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>这样的类一般叫做dto，也就是数据传输对象，继承Dish类，在里面新加一个关于Flavors的list，用于接收数据</p><p>那么前端的数据就可以保存在这样一个类中</p><p>接下来就是如何对数据库进行操作了</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-meta">@Transactional</span> <span class="hljs-comment">//启动事务</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">saveWithFlavor</span><span class="hljs-params">(DishDto dishDto)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">//保存菜品基本信息到dish</span><br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.save(dishDto);<br><br>        <span class="hljs-type">Long</span> <span class="hljs-variable">dishId</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> dishDto.getId();<br><br>        List&lt;DishFlavor&gt; flavors = dishDto.getFlavors();<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">/*利用Lambda表达式，取出flavors里的每一个元素赋值给item，然后对item进行操作后将item返回，返回之后将返回的item转成一个List给flavors*/</span><br>        flavors = flavors.stream().map((item) -&gt; &#123;<br>            item.setDishId(dishId);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> item;<br>        &#125;).collect((Collectors.toList()));<br><br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">//保存菜品口味数据</span><br>        dishFlavorService.saveBatch(flavors);<br>    &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>这里涉及到增加操作，所以需要加上事务注解</p><p>因为dishdto这个类是继承于dish的，所以其中的数据都是存在于dish的，直接进行保存即可</p><p>接下来是flavors，对于flavors来说，缺少一个id，可以选择遍历这个list，然后给它设置id</p><p>这里选择用一个Lambda表达式，取出其中的每一项，然后对每一项设置id，最后将设置好的item返回</p><p>最终将所有的item进行组合到一个list里面重新赋值给flavors，这样所有的工作就完成了</p><p>这就是关于多表操作关于新增的部分</p></blockquote><h2 id="多表分页查询部分"><a href="#多表分页查询部分" class="headerlink" title="多表分页查询部分"></a>多表分页查询部分</h2><blockquote><p>在显示菜品数据的同时，需要显示分类数据，这里就涉及到了关于dish和category的操作</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-meta">@GetMapping(&quot;/page&quot;)</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> R&lt;Page&gt; <span class="hljs-title function_">page</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> page,<span class="hljs-type">int</span> pageSize,String name)</span>&#123;<br>        Page&lt;Dish&gt; pageInfo = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Page</span>&lt;&gt;(page, pageSize);<br>        Page&lt;DishDto&gt; dishDtoPage = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Page</span>&lt;&gt;();<br>        LambdaQueryWrapper&lt;Dish&gt; queryWrapper = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">LambdaQueryWrapper</span>&lt;&gt;();<br>        queryWrapper.like(name != <span class="hljs-literal">null</span>, Dish::getName, name);<br>        queryWrapper.orderByDesc(Dish::getUpdateTime);<br>        dishService.page(pageInfo, queryWrapper);<br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">//对象拷贝</span><br>        BeanUtils.copyProperties(pageInfo, dishDtoPage,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;records&quot;</span>);<br><br>        List&lt;Dish&gt; records = pageInfo.getRecords();<br>        List&lt;DishDto&gt; list = records.stream().map((item)-&gt;&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">DishDto</span> <span class="hljs-variable">dishDto</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">DishDto</span>();<br><br>            BeanUtils.copyProperties(item, dishDto);<br><br>            <span class="hljs-type">Long</span> <span class="hljs-variable">categoryId</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> item.getCategoryId();  <span class="hljs-comment">//分类id</span><br>            <span class="hljs-type">Category</span> <span class="hljs-variable">category</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> categoryService.getById(categoryId);<br>            <span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">categoryName</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> category.getName();<br>            dishDto.setCategoryName(categoryName);<br><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> dishDto;<br>        &#125;).collect(Collectors.toList());<br><br>        dishDtoPage.setRecords(list);<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> R.success(dishDtoPage);<br>    &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>这里首先不变的是构造分页构造器</p><p>不同点是这次需要两个分页构造器，一个是dish表的，一个是dishdto表的</p><p>因为最后要返回的是一个dishdto的数据</p><p>这里第一步是先对dish表进行分页查询，将数据线存储到pageInfo中</p><p>接下来是要将pageInfo中的数据复制到dishDtoPage中</p><p>用到了一个工具类，BeanUtils.copyProperties，这是一个对象拷贝的工具类，第一个参数是被复制对象，第二个参数是需要复制的对象，第三个参数可以设置不去赋值哪个字段，这里忽略records字段，因为records字段中包含就是分页数据，但是这些数据其实是dish的，我们要手动设置成地上dto的</p><p>所以接下来还是用Lambda表达式，将pageInfo中的每一个dish对象取出来，先将dish中的数据复制到dishDto中，然后根据dishId在category表中查出categoryName字段，手动赋值，最后将此list用set方法存储到dishDtoPage中进行返回</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
    
